* ''Rise of Prussia'' (2010)
* ''Revolution Under Siege'' (2010)
* ''[[Pride of Nations]]'' (2011)
* ''Alea Jacta Est'' (2012)
* ''Birth of Rome'' (2013)
* ''Civil War 2'' (2013)
* ''Hannibal: Terror of Rome'' (2014)
* ''To End All Wars'' (2014)
* ''Thirty Years War'' (2015)
* ''Wars of Napoleon'' (2015)

